                            <comment id="10691" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Tue, 27 Jul 2004 03:42:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Indeed, that&apos;s bug caused by the new extended child bean definition concept. I&apos;ve added a check to PropertiesBeanDefinitionReader, to just apply the defaultParentBean setting if we&apos;re not dealing with that parent bean definition itself.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the report!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
